                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <addressee>Rev Dr I. Leeser</addressee>\n                <placeName>Phila</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <date>20 Feb</date>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><placeName>Washington, D. C</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <add>ב\"ה אסתר תורמת תכסי</add>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <add>וואשינגטאן עיר הבירה</add>\n            </p>\n            <p>Dear Doctor!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I learned there are 2 Candidates<lb/> already for the Surgeonship of\n                the Jewish Hospital<lb/> before its being published yet. I do not desire to<lb/>\n                compete if there is but little chance, and would beg<lb/> you to inform me whether\n                you deem it worthwhile<lb/> that I should run the risk of not being elected, as I\n                have<lb/> no estimate of the Salary and would execute efforts to<lb/> get it, only\n                if it yields a good chance.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The points I could honestly lay stress upon for<lb/> competition are\n                chiefly my thorough knowledge of Hos-<lb/>pital routine, language &amp; acquaintance\n                with the leading<lb/> Physicians of <placeName>Phila</placeName> in critical cases\n                for consultation<lb/> the particular empirical attention I devoted to the peculiar<lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">types of disease</hi> as they appear <hi rend=\"underline\">in\n                    this country</hi><lb/> different from those abroad, how they manifest\n                themselves<lb/> in foreigners etc and if also of some avail—<lb/> my acquaintance\n                with the <hi rend=\"underline\">virtues</hi><add>?</add> desirable to</p>\n            "
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3pc2tr8d/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
