                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n            <p>be familiar with for a Jewish Hospital<lb/> Surgeon.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">With regards from my family</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Your</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Obdt servt</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Dr L Schoney</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <placeName>office 262 Pa Av</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p>PS.</p>\n            <p>Please to send me one of your last<lb/> “Occident,” that I can cut conveniently<lb/>\n                for the same my treatise on the “Hag<lb/>drean”<add>?</add> entitled\n                    “<sic>Sanatary</sic> institutions<lb/> of the Hebrews” which is as yet in\n                loose<lb/> sheets and not arranged properly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">LS</persName>\n            </p>\n            "
                  },
